<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>假设租房 X 年，对比买房是否更划算</title>
    <style>
        :root { --buy-color: #3498db; --rent-color: #f1c40f; --text-main: #2c3e50; }
        body { font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; color: var(--text-main); margin: 0; padding: 20px; font-size: 15px; }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        
        header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 15px; }
        .logic-note { background: #fdfefe; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.6; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
        
        .main-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px; }
        .card { padding: 22px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; position: relative; }
        .buy-card { border-top: 5px solid var(--buy-color); background: #fbfdff; }
        .rent-card { border-top: 5px solid var(--rent-color); background: #fffdf9; }
        
        h3 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333; }
        .input-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
        label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 6px; color: #555; }
        .sub-label { font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; color: #888; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        input, select { width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; }
        input:focus { border-color: var(--buy-color); outline: none; background: #fff; }
        
        .tax-link { color: #3498db; text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 8px; border-bottom: 1px dashed #3498db; }
        
        button { width: 100%; padding: 16px; background: #2c3e50; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 30px; transition: 0.2s; }
        button:hover { background: #34495e; transform: translateY(-1px); }

        /* 结果展示 */
        #result-area { margin-top: 30px; display: none; }
        .result-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
        .res-box { padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; }
        .buy-res { background: #eef7ff; border: 1px solid #d4eaff; }
        .rent-res { background: #fff9e6; border: 1px solid #f9ebbe; }
        .highlight { font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; display: block; margin: 10px 0; color: #2c3e50; }
        .analysis-report { margin-top: 25px; padding: 25px; background: #f4fbf9; border-radius: 12px; line-height: 1.8; border-left: 6px solid #2ecc71; box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .main-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>假设租房 X 年，对比买房是否更划算</h1>
        <p>基于深圳 2026 市场规则的资产价值模拟工具 (最终版)</p>
    </header>

    <div class="logic-note">
        <strong>📝 核心计算逻辑：</strong><br>
        • <b>买房路径：</b>$X$ 年后资产 = [买入价 × (1 + 最终总涨跌幅)] - [欠银行的剩余本金] - [买入时的一次性税费及装修] - [累计支付利息]。<br>
        • <b>租房路径：</b>$X$ 年后资产 = [原本准备买房的本金拿去理财 $X$ 年的本息和] - [ $X$ 年累计支付的租金支出]。<br>
        • <b>对冲项：</b>物业费、维修费在两端对冲，不计入差额。
    </div>

    <div class="main-grid">
        <div class="card buy-card">
            <h3>🏠 买房投入参考</h3>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>房屋总价 (万元)</label>
                <input type="number" id="price" value="500">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>房屋类型</label>
                <select id="houseType" onchange="updateDefaultTax()">
                    <option value="new">深圳新房 (默认 1.5% 契税)</option>
                    <option value="second">深圳二手房 (默认 5% 综合税费)</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>
                    综合税费比例 (%)
                    <a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/b1NR1U_jTrsHI4q29EQ8UA" target="_blank" class="tax-link">深圳税费政策查询 ↗</a>
                </label>
                <input type="number" id="taxRate" value="1.5">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>装修/软装投入 (万元)</label>
                <input type="number" id="decor" value="20">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>首付比例 (%)</label>
                <input type="number" id="downRate" value="30">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>房贷利率 (年化 %)</label>
                <input type="number" id="loanRate" value="3.5">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>X 年后房价最终总涨跌幅 (%)</label>
                <span class="sub-label">相对于当前买入价的一次性变化</span>
                <input type="number" id="totalPriceChange" value="0" placeholder="例如：-20 代表持有期满时房价跌了20%">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card rent-card">
            <h3>🔑 租房决策变量</h3>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>预设租房/对比年限 (X年)</label>
                <input type="number" id="X" value="10">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>理财年化收益率 (%)</label>
                <span class="sub-label">假设原买房资金用于投资后的平均年盈亏</span>
                <input type="number" id="investRate" value="2.5">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>当前同地段月租金 (元)</label>
                <input type="number" id="rent" value="10000">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>预期租金年均涨跌幅 (%)</label>
                <input type="number" id="rentChange" value="0">
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 40px; line-height: 1.4;">
                * 理财本金 = [买房首付 + 税费 + 装修]。<br>
                * 系统将对比 $X$ 年后“卖房所得”与“现金积累”的净值。
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <button onclick="calculateFinal()">🚀 运行对比分析</button>

    <div id="result-area">
        <div class="result-grid">
            <div class="res-box buy-res">
                <span>方案一：买房并持有 $X$ 年后净资产</span>
                <span class="highlight" id="res_buy_net">--</span>
                <small id="res_buy_detail" style="color:#777;"></small>
            </div>
            <div class="res-box rent-res">
                <span>方案二：租房 $X$ 年后理财净资产</span>
                <span class="highlight" id="res_rent_net">--</span>
                <small id="res_rent_detail" style="color:#777;"></small>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="analysis-report" id="report"></div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
function updateDefaultTax() {
    const type = document.getElementById('houseType').value;
    const taxInput = document.getElementById('taxRate');
    taxInput.value = (type === 'new') ? 1.5 : 5.0;
}

function calculateFinal() {
    const X = parseFloat(document.getElementById('X').value);
    const P = parseFloat(document.getElementById('price').value);
    const taxRate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('taxRate').value) / 100;
    const decor = parseFloat(document.getElementById('decor').value);
    const dr = parseFloat(document.getElementById('downRate').value) / 100;
    const lr = parseFloat(document.getElementById('loanRate').value) / 100 / 12;
    const totalPc = parseFloat(document.getElementById('totalPriceChange').value) / 100;

    const r0 = parseFloat(document.getElementById('rent').value);
    const rc = parseFloat(document.getElementById('rentChange').value) / 100;
    const ir = parseFloat(document.getElementById('investRate').value) / 100 / 12;

    // --- 买房模型 ---
    const initialTax = P * taxRate;
    const totalInitialBuy = (P * dr) + initialTax + decor; 
    
    const principal = P * (1 - dr);
    const months = 30 * 12;
    const mPay = (principal * lr * Math.pow(1 + lr, months)) / (Math.pow(1 + lr, months) - 1);
    
    let totalInt = 0;
    let remP = principal;
    for(let i=0; i<X*12; i++){
        let intPart = remP * lr;
        totalInt += intPart;
        remP -= (mPay - intPart);
    }
    // 关键修正：直接使用最终总涨跌幅计算房价
    const finalHValue = P * (1 + totalPc); 
    const buyNet = finalHValue - remP - initialTax - decor - totalInt;

    // --- 租房模型 ---
    let currentCap = totalInitialBuy; 
    let totalRent = 0;
    for(let i=0; i<X*12; i++){
        currentCap *= (1 + ir);
        let currentRent = r0 * Math.pow(1 + rc, Math.floor(i/12));
        totalRent += currentRent;
    }
    const rentNet = currentCap - (totalRent / 10000);

    // --- 渲染 ---
    document.getElementById('result-area').style.display = 'block';
    document.getElementById('res_buy_net').innerText = buyNet.toFixed(2) + " 万元";
    document.getElementById('res_buy_detail').innerText = `已扣除${totalInt.toFixed(1)}万利息及${initialTax.toFixed(1)}万税费`;
    document.getElementById('res_rent_net').innerText = rentNet.toFixed(2) + " 万元";
    document.getElementById('res_rent_detail').innerText = `含${(currentCap - totalInitialBuy).toFixed(1)}万理财收益扣除租金`;

    // --- 分析报告 ---
    const diff = buyNet - rentNet;
    const report = document.getElementById('report');
    let analysis = `<strong>📈 财务决策深度解读：</strong><br>`;
    
    if (diff > 0) {
        analysis += `🚩 <strong>结论：在当前假设下，买房持有更划算。</strong><br>到第 ${X} 年时，买房方案形成的“房产净值”比租房方案多出 <b>${diff.toFixed(2)}</b> 万元。<br>`;
    } else {
        analysis += `🚩 <strong>结论：在当前假设下，选择租房更划算。</strong><br>到第 ${X} 年时，通过租房并保留现金流理财，你最终拥有的资金比买房方案多出 <b>${Math.abs(diff).toFixed(2)}</b> 万元。<br>`;
    }

    analysis += `<br>🔎 <strong>关键诊断：</strong><ul>`;
    analysis += `<li><b>资产保值要求：</b>若想买房不亏于租房，房价在 ${X} 年后的总跌幅不能超过某临界点（你可以尝试修改涨跌幅参数来寻找这个平衡点）。</li>`;
    analysis += `<li><b>利息成本：</b>你这 ${X} 年累计为银行贡献了 <b>${totalInt.toFixed(1)}</b> 万元利息。</li>`;
    analysis += `<li><b>理财门槛：</b>租房方案依赖于你那 <b>${totalInitialBuy.toFixed(1)}</b> 万元原始本金每年 <b>${(ir*12*100).toFixed(1)}%</b> 的理财表现。</li>`;
    analysis += `</ul>`;

    report.innerHTML = analysis;
    window.scrollTo({ top: document.body.scrollHeight, behavior: 'smooth' });
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
